"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-caitlin-clark-brittney-griner-paris-olympics-team-b2559244.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Critics of the decision call it 'dumb,' a 'horrible vision,' and an 'opportunity wasted'  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Caitlin Clark, the rookiemaking wavesin theWNBA, will not be joining theUS national teamwhen it travels to theParisOlympics, according to reports.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sources close to the situation revealed that theall-time college scoring leaderwill be staying home, according toNBC News.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the source, which spoke exclusively to the broadcaster, the team will be made up of 12 veterans - meaning Clark will not be in tow.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the women who is said to be joining the team is Phoenix Mercury centerBrittney Griner, who spent 10 months detained in Russia on alleged drug possession charges before she was returned to the US in a prisoner swap in December.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res