n\": 1462, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Mystics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.277271261159567e-21, \"text\": \"Washington Mystics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Mystics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Mystics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite her accolades - she was named the WNBA's rookie of the month in May - Clark, like any rookie, is still perfecting her game.\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.396855956451774e-19, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has only hit 32.7 per cent of her 3 point attempts in her short professional career, and have given up an average of five turnovers per game, which is the most in the league.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even still, there are some who are baffled by the team's reported decision not to bring her along.\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bartsool Sports founder Dave Portnoy said the decision, if true, is the \\\"dumbest thing I have ever heard\\\" in a post on X.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1925, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Portnoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.295308490844975e-15, \"text\": \"Portnoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Portnoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Portnoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"How dumb are these people?\\\"\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Portnoy asked.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Never complain about women salaries ever again.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make that team fly commercial.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unreal dumb.\\\"\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said Clark's performance makes watching her games \\\"appointment TV.\\\"\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd rather watch grass grow, I'd rather watch paint dry.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd rather watch dirt just be moved around because Caitlin Clark is not on the team,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If she's there, it's appointment TV.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You people, whoever did this, take your brain, put it in a museum and study it for how dumb you are.\\\"\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Justin Termine, a Sirus XM commentator, said it was foolish not to include one of the most talked-about players in the sport at a time when the league is trying to expand its viewership, theNew York Postreports.\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2548, \"end\": 2550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sirius_XM\", \"score\": 0.951306436960787, \"rank\": 0.05118599133493066, \"text\": \"XM\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sirius_XM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sirius_XM\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even if she stinks, which she does not, that's horrible vision,\\\" he posted.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox Sports host Colin Cowherd shared those sentiments, arguing that the Olympics and the league were leaving money on the table by not including Clark.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2815, \"end\": 2825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999030665141, \"rank\": 7.738017444659115e-08, \"text\": \"Fox Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2831, \"end\": 2844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Cowherd\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Cowherd\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2722764\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13590141\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Cowherd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Cowherd\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Christian Laettner made the Dream Team.\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2969, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Laettner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christian Laettner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Laettner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Laettner\"}, {\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9976283543451605, \"rank\": 0.0023772837295367977, \"text\": \"Dream Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_United_States_men's_Olympic_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ca